AMAZON is proud to partner with @pgshiksha, committed to bridge the #InvisibleGap

 What is the #InvisibleGap? - The learning level of a child is not always equal to their grade level in school. This is the learning gap that most of us can’t see. 6 crore children affected by learning gaps are unable to cope up in class and many of them eventually drop out of school. 

@pgshiksha is working to help lakhs like Bindiya to overcome this learning gap through innovative remedial learning solutions.
#PGSHIKSHA #InvisibleGap #LearningGap
